      {
        "text": "和平",
        "label": "LOC"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_013_048_000172",
    "sentence": "下部議，從之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_013_048_000173",
    "sentence": "遂班師。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_013_048_000174",
    "sentence": "捷聞，賜璽書襃賞，餘功賞賚有差。",
